PN,41301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FI've been to the Royal Courts of
OL,7,FJustice in Belfast many times - mostly
OL,8,Ffor judicial review hearings. But I'd
OL,9,Fnever attended a Court of Appeal Case
OL,10,F- until recently.
OL,12,FThat's the next court appellants, as
OL,13,Fthey are known, take their case after
OL,14,Fthe High Court or Crown Court if they
OL,15,Fdisagree with the decision or verdict
OL,16,Fdelivered there.
OL,18,FThree judges listen to arguments on
OL,19,Fboth sides before returning their
OL,20,Ffindings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FIn this case the chief justice - Dame
OL,7,FSiobhan Keegan - Northern Ireland's
OL,8,Fmost senior judge was flanked by two
OL,9,Fother senior judges - Lord Justice
OL,10,FTreacy and Mr Justice O'Hara.
OL,12,FThere were a total of nine barristers
OL,13,Fin court - two I observed representing
OL,14,Feach party in the case.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FIt was good access in itself and
OL,7,Ffascinating too - about a female same
OL,8,Fsex couple who were arguing the non-
OL,9,Fbiological parent in the partnership
OL,10,Fshould be named on the birth
OL,11,Fcertificate of the child they are
OL,12,Fresponsible for.
OL,14,FIn the end and after a couple of weeks
OL,15,Fthe court rejected their appeal
OL,16,Fagainst the decision not to grant a
OL,17,Fdeclaration of parentage to the non
OL,18,Fbirth mother concluding that it would
OL,19,F'circumvent the statutory scheme' and
OL,20,Fbe 'manifestly contrary to public
OL,21,Fpolicy.'
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FThe next step for the couple if they
OL,7,Fso choose would be to apply for leave
OL,8,Fto take their case to the Supreme
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FWhat was especially pertinent about
OL,12,Fthe case though, as well as being a
OL,13,Ftimely reminder of the increasing
OL,14,Fdiversity and societal shifts in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, was that it fell
OL,16,Fwithin family law - a significant
OL,17,Fbranch of civil rather than criminal
OL,18,Flaw.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FAnd the only reason I as a journalist
OL,7,Fwas allowed to be there was that it
OL,8,Fwas part of a pilot exploring media
OL,9,Faccess to this part of the legal
OL,10,Fprocess.
OL,12,FI had to sign a stringent transparency
OL,13,Forder telling me what I could and
OL,14,Fcouldn't do and any of the parties
OL,15,Fcould object to my presence.
OL,17,FThe same order was checked once by
OL,18,Fsecurity ahead of the hearing and then
OL,19,Fagain before entering the court for
OL,20,Fthe judgement.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FThat is not required in the criminal
OL,7,Fjustice system - or other parts of
OL,8,Fcivil law.
OL,10,FWe as journalists are used to
OL,11,Fattending and reporting on these
OL,12,Fcases. In fact it provides us with a
OL,13,Fsignificant amount of our content.
OL,15,FThe openness and transparency around
OL,16,Fboth the Magistrates and Crown courts
OL,17,Fis well established, governed by a
OL,18,Fvery strict set of rules which we
OL,19,Flearn in our training and if breached,
OL,20,Fhave very serious consequences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FIt is a cornerstone of this part of
OL,7,Fthe legal process and vitally
OL,8,Fimportant to maintain trust in the
OL,9,Fsystem: the old adage of justice being
OL,10,Fdone and being seen to be done.
OL,12,FBut that's not been the case with
OL,13,Ffamily courts which handle the most
OL,14,Fsensitive areas of people's lives.
OL,16,FPrimarily it's argued that privacy
OL,17,Fprotects the children and other
OL,18,Fvulnerable people involved in what can
OL,19,Fbe very complex cases.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FA pilot in England and Wales recently
OL,7,Fled to a permanent change to the law
OL,8,Fso in those jurisdictions as long as
OL,9,Fyou are an accredited journalist and
OL,10,Ffollow regulations around ensuring the
OL,11,Fanonymity of the parties involved you
OL,12,Fare entitled to report on what you see
OL,13,Fand hear in court.
OL,15,FWe in Northern Ireland are not at that
OL,16,Fpoint - yet.
OL,18,FBut we are in the process of exploring
OL,19,Fthat potential.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FThere have been publicly-acknowledged
OL,7,Fmiscarriages of justice in family
OL,8,Fcourts in other jurisdictions and I
OL,9,Fhave many examples of parents claiming
OL,10,Fthey have been unfairly treated. They
OL,11,Fbelieve media access to the courts
OL,12,Fwould go some way to change that.
OL,14,FThat evidence is not merely anecdotal
OL,15,F- a wide ranging report commissioned
OL,16,Fby the victims of crime commissioner
OL,17,Fand published at the end of last year
OL,18,Ffound that there were significant
OL,19,Fchallenges faced in particular by
OL,20,Fvictims of domestic violence in family
OL,21,Fcourts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FThey described feeling unheard and
OL,7,Funsupported, with some describing the
OL,8,Fprocess as retraumatising.
OL,10,FThat report called for an urgent need
OL,11,Ffor reform and set out a raft of
OL,12,Frecommendations including a
OL,13,Fpresumption against contact operating
OL,14,Fin cases where domestic violence is
OL,15,Festablished which was one of the
OL,16,Fbiggest concerns of the women who
OL,17,Freached out to me.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FThe chief justice is an expert in this
OL,7,Farea of law. She practised as a family
OL,8,Fbarrister for many years before
OL,9,Fbecoming a judge.
OL,11,FDame Siobhan Keegan told me she
OL,12,Frecognised the devastating impact of
OL,13,Fdomestic violence on victims and
OL,14,Fwanted to ensure they are supported
OL,15,Fthrough the process. She added she was
OL,16,Fbeing lobbied by both women and men
OL,17,Fand insisted there is ' no hierarchy
OL,18,Fof victims' and that familial
OL,19,Fbreakdown is complicated and almost
OL,20,Falways in her words 'messy'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FShe's long advocated for transparency
OL,7,Fand greater access to our court system
OL,8,Fto help the public better understand
OL,9,Fthe complex decisions that judges make
OL,10,Fand has worked with the Department of
OL,11,FJustice to consider legislative
OL,12,Fchanges to support media access to
OL,13,Ffamily cases but says that access has
OL,14,Fto be balanced with the welfare of the
OL,15,Fchild or children involved.
OL,17,FFamily law concerns deeply private
OL,18,Fmatters so I can understand there may
OL,19,Fbe resistance to letting reporters
OL,20,Finto the courtroom.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FBut it is also a significant area of
OL,7,Fthe law affecting the most vulnerable
OL,8,Fin our society, in particular
OL,9,Fchildren, so striking a balance
OL,10,Fbetween that privacy and the public
OL,11,Finterest is crucial.
OL,13,FIt's important to stress the case I
OL,14,Fgot access to did NOT involve domestic
OL,15,Fabuse.
OL,17,FThe reason we applied to attend it was
OL,18,Fthat it was a one day hearing - we are
OL,19,Fa small team and this type of
OL,20,Freporting takes a lot of commitment of
OL,21,Fboth resources and time.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FWhile this pilot has been a helpful
OL,7,Fstep forward, it has also been a
OL,8,Flimited form of transparency - we are
OL,9,Fgiven a list of cases we can apply to
OL,10,Fattend so it's not really true
OL,11,Fopenness and we were bound by a strict
OL,12,Forder which warns: 'if you fail to
OL,13,Fcomply you may be found guilty of
OL,14,Fcontempt of court and may be sent to
OL,15,Fprison or fined or your assets, may be
OL,16,Fseized.'
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781894897
OL,3,CShining a light on the family court
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FNevertheless as a public service
OL,7,Fbroadcaster and trusted regional news
OL,8,Fprovider we recognise the role we play
OL,9,Fand the value of scrutinising systems
OL,10,Fwhich affect the communities we
OL,11,Freflect.
OL,13,FHaving reputable reporters in the
OL,14,Ffamily courtroom to observe what's
OL,15,Fgoing on can only be a healthy
OL,16,Fdevelopment.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
